		<DIV ALIGN="CENTER"><FONT SIZE="+2">Mage Armor</FONT><BR>
Zone : Temple of Solusek Ro<BR><BR>
<TABLE CELLSPACING = 0 CELLPADDING = 0 BORDER = 0>
<TR><TD><FONT SIZE="1" FACE="ariel"><B>Updated :</B> November 23 1999</FONT><BR><BR>

Joyce will make 3 articles of magician armor. <BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=107">Clay Bracelet:</A> He needs all 4 runes of clay. 3 come from Gnomish Necros in Rathe Mtns in the two towers (Bindlegrob, Sindlegrob and Tindlegrob). The other comes from the Goblin Headmaster in OOT (by a tent on the oracle's island). The 3 necros in the mountains are in 2 different spots one close to the lake zone and 2 together closer to the Ferrott zone. <BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=108">Earthen Boots:</A> Stone marker (glyphed guard in Castle Mistmoore), Heart of Stone (stone skeleton in Lake Rathetear), Soiled Boots (froglok Tonta Knight in Guk), and a Cat's Eye Agate.<BR><BR> 

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=109">Circlet of Mist:</A> Globe of mist (festering hag in Unrest), Water Ring (aqua goblin tidal lord in Dagnor's),  Ring of Evoluoy (large alligator in Cazic-Thule), and a Sapphire. <BR><BR>

<B>NEW:</B> Click <A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/files/mage_armor.zip">HERE</A> to download a single page checklist for this quest that is in Word '97 format. A handy tool to help organize all the steps involved.<BR><BR>
</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
